data.description: Sweeping ocean views in this single level home in Pualani Estates.   This Hawaiian haven features a single-level layout that encapsulates the essence of island living with its panoramic ocean views. Three bedrooms provide private retreats, including a primary suite with ocean views. A two-car garage offers convenience, while the central AC system ensures comfort in every corner of the house. The open floor plan combines the kitchen, dining and living area to insure that everyone is included in this wonderful home!   Located in Pualani Estates, the neighborhood features a park, low HOA fees, and easy access to the heart of town and shopping.
